webwork-tex.statement: Let \(\mathbf{a} = (10, 9, 10)\) and \(\mathbf{b} = (2, 4, 8)\) be vectors. \leavevmode\\\relax Compute the cross product \(\mathbf{a} \times \mathbf{b}\). \leavevmode\\\relax \leavevmode\\\relax \(\mathbf{a} \times \mathbf{b}=\)(\mbox{\parbox[t]{3ex}{\hrulefill}}, \mbox{\parbox[t]{3ex}{\hrulefill}}, \mbox{\parbox[t]{3ex}{\hrulefill}})
